■ 終身學習的態度
強化終身自我學習意願之能力。 Habit of lifelong learning
 

課程概述 Course Description
       向學生介紹 (1) 幹細胞、 發育生物學和組織修復，以及 (2) 現代技術用於幹細胞與再生醫學中的當代和更新基礎與臨床研究。 To help students to understand the mechanisms and pathogenesis  of neurodegenerative diseases; to learn the experimental designs of neurodegenerative diseases.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
To help student to understand the mechanisms of neurodegenerative diseases.To help student to understand the pathogenesis of neurodegenerative diseases.To help student to learn the experimental designs of neurodegenerative diseases. 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Course orientation/Introduction2Nerve cells and neural tissue organization3Nerve cells and neural diseases4Synaptic degeneration and neuronal death in Alzheimer's disease (I)5Synaptic degeneration and neuronal death in Alzheimer's disease (II)6Pathogenesis of amyotrophic lateral sclerosis7春假8Mechanisms of neuronal apoptosis and excitotoxicity9Midterm exam10Pathogenesis of ischemic stroke (I)11Pathogenesis of ischemic stroke (II)12Mechanisms of neuronal death in Huntington's disease (I)13Mechanisms of neuronal death in Huntington's disease (II)14Parkinson's disease (I)15Parkinson's disease (II)16Spinal cord injury (I)17Spinal cord injury (II)18Final exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


